Routes from the far LEFT of the crag towards the right (i.e. back towards the car park) Vertical, 1 minute flat walk, Early morning shade & Late Afternoon shade This is one of Montagu's most popular crags due to the easier grade of routes and the 1 minute walk-in. Legoland is child friendly and dogs are allowed. From Montagu direction: Drive towards Ashton/Cape Town, about 1km after the tunnel you will see the
textAfterTable: The Far Side The Far Side is on the opposite side of the road (R62). Park in the parking area before Legoland and walk over the bridge (river) towards Montagu, then jump over the small fence to walk to the crag ahead of you on your right.
